{"tid":777640,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"明愛醫院醫生遭男子揮拳襲擊","createTime":"2018-08-13T05:27:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-13T09:21:45.000Z","uid":13468,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2cf4c809a8ce0577dbcb4660bf7c0ec729f80f8f","tid":777640,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T05:27:44.000Z","msg":"明愛醫院醫生遭男子揮拳襲擊<br />\n<br />\n明愛醫院早上有病人襲擊醫生。早上7時許，保安發現一名52歲男子在急症室大堂倒下，然後帶該名男子登記候診，其間男子突然跌倒，撞傷頭部。其後33歲姓黃急症室醫生，為該名男子檢查時，男子突然向醫生腹部揮拳，院方隨即報警。警員到場調查，醫生報稱未有受傷，決定不追究。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180813/s00001/1534130480874\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180813%2Fs00001%2F1534130480874&d=gRnHp2AfHxnihZFnxWWf%2BMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=6d4b85fa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180813%2Fs00001%2F1534130480874&h=1c2ef127\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180813/s00001/1534130480874</a>"},{"pid":"dab9fdd046c1e4b7367609f6af05732d62a259b6","tid":777640,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T05:34:30.000Z","msg":"世界情色王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23a794ca7c949d74191319e47b07ab5fdf5a5aaf","tid":777640,"uid":39576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T05:37:45.000Z","msg":"香港咁多痴線佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a82c19ba8768a853b443974a9c4ddd4ab36aaa63","tid":777640,"uid":66527,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T05:39:11.000Z","msg":"每日150黎"},{"pid":"ecc963bd78576601929cfc2cb5da93e662488dd4","tid":777640,"uid":55488,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T06:14:30.000Z","msg":